data.description: Welcome to this 2-bedroom townhouse in the Graniteville area of Staten Island. This cozy and convenient place to live has brand new grayscale flooring and the fireplace in the Living room. Dining Room combo add a charming touch. Plus, having an in-unit washer/dryer for multitasking is a great feature. The upstairs layout with two lofty bedrooms and ample storage for your necessities.Amenities such as playground, pool, and snow removal make it even more appealing. Assigned parking and plenty of guess spaces assures that you, and your family always have a place to park. conveniently located near Richmond Avenue, expressway , and shopping plaza's adds to the convenience.   Schedule a showing today !
